title: Fortuneteller's Secret Recipe
overview: Na Rae is a kindergarten teacher who suddenly develops the ability of a shaman fortuneteller while praying at a church one day. She gives up her life as a teacher and finds fame and wealth as a fortuneteller. But as time passes, her skills begin to fade. When Na Rae discovers a mysterious app called "T-Scope," can she use it to regain her fortunetelling fame?
